snippet.title: "I Lied" Amber Heard Apologises to Johnny Depp!
snippet.description:
"I Lied" Amber Heard Apologises to Johnny Depp 
In the last few years, reports about the case of Johnny Depp and Amber Heard has saturated the internet. The question between the two, as many want to find out, is who is the true perpetrator. As there are different accounts from each side as the case continues, we realize that fingers are only pointing at Amber Heard as more information is being produced.
